  "description": "<i>Scentipede</i> is a <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?gamegroup=Centipede+variants\">Centipede clone</a> for the MSX.<br><br>A long centipede-like insect being gradually moves down from the top of the screen, its route affected by randomly placed trees / mushrooms. The player must shoot all segments of the creature before they reach the bottom of the screen. <br><br>When the creature is shot in the middle it breaks into two independently moving pieces that makes the game more complex.<br><br>In addition to the creature the player must avoid spiders that randomly track across the screen.\n",
